{"tid":2116592,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"聯國秘書長促改革安理會及世銀  「武肺如Ｘ光機揭全球不公」","createTime":"2020-07-20T09:00:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-20T10:20:02.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"e02bc9830cfa7d7587d1443fb724e65639ae0e20","tid":2116592,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T09:00:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20200720/SP5RQYQTRBDAKUVCYMYZ3G3KVY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200720%2FSP5RQYQTRBDAKUVCYMYZ3G3KVY%2F&d=P0F1PEBUYD2FcM6JX1v4ze6cow1LS9WQT%2BeJ8I%2F17x8%3D&h=939b0821\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200720%2FSP5RQYQTRBDAKUVCYMYZ3G3KVY%2F&h=302635bd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20200720/SP5RQYQTRBDAKUVCYMYZ3G3KVY/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n聯國秘書長促改革安理會及世銀 <br />\n「武肺如Ｘ光機揭全球不公」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/7FzPEV3DFf18htWkhsq7PbUAc2Y=/190x138/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/4S7BFPQMRQYRFGTYHVJU5KYL2M.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F7FzPEV3DFf18htWkhsq7PbUAc2Y%3D%2F190x138%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F4S7BFPQMRQYRFGTYHVJU5KYL2M.gif&h=8e9543a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n聯合國把曼德拉生辰定性為反思和推動全球平等與和平的日子。美聯社<br />\n<br />\n聯合國秘書長古特雷斯（Antonio Guterres）於前日「曼德拉國際日」發表演講，狠批全球不平等已大有改善的「謊言、妄想和謬誤」，促趁武漢肺炎的「臨界點」，推動「新社會契約」和「全球新政」消除種族和貧富不公，改革安理會和世界銀行等國際組織 。<br />\n<br />\n前日是南非已故總統曼德拉102歲生忌，聯合國2009年起將他的生辰定為「曼德拉國際日」，古特雷斯於美國紐約聯合國總部經網絡發表演說，措詞少有地嚴厲，說武漢肺炎危機，揭示長久以來社會結構潛在的裂痕，包括醫療系統不足、社會保障差異、結構性不平等、環境轉差以及氣候危機等。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n轟發展國囤積醫療物資<br />\n<br />\n他形容武漢肺炎有如Ｘ光機，........................................<br />\n<br />\n古特雷斯又提到全球財富極不平均，「26個最富有的人，手握全球半數財富」，種族、性別、地位和出生地亦造成不平等；去年反性侵浪朝#MeToo，以至近期美國黑人民權運動，都是部份人看清事實後的怒吼。<br />\n<br />\n他指非洲發展中國家是「雙重受害者」，.....................................<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n稱殖民主義殘存 非洲受害<br />\n<br />\n古特雷斯說，全球疫情下面臨二戰以來最大環球衰退，但危中亦有機：「不平等是從最高層開始，即是國際組織，要處理不平等，必須先改革這些組織。」<br />\n<br />\n他促請各國推行「新社會契約」和「全球新政」，.....................................<br />\n<br />\n他又呼籲個人和企業應平均攤分社會保障，................................<br />\n<br />\n美聯社／英國《衞報》<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/PT2KtF6p_D92NlG_mzd6ZT1Rrlc=/190x144/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/IDR2JCE4RPXBUL32SPMDSBDHC4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FPT2KtF6p_D92NlG_mzd6ZT1Rrlc%3D%2F190x144%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FIDR2JCE4RPXBUL32SPMDSBDHC4.gif&h=281d6b8a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n前天古特雷斯在網上發表今年的曼德拉國際日演講。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/WK4yWxL3SFWDk_2ctuug37PdA0o=/190x144/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/UUHDKWNKMW3ZO2AWAANZMYMIFM.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FWK4yWxL3SFWDk_2ctuug37PdA0o%3D%2F190x144%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FUUHDKWNKMW3ZO2AWAANZMYMIFM.gif&h=71548d8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n古特雷斯強調要透過加強教育資源以改善全球不平等。"},{"pid":"9c08ffa444b58e4d1e39cc4202082904ca6d2cce","tid":2116592,"uid":15605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T09:14:59.000Z","msg":"部x光機咪就照到支那呢個大毒瘤出黎囉"},{"pid":"5baf209e76c8ffb80a5e7c6d13a80f14ae606901","tid":2116592,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T09:20:24.000Z","msg":"想借啲意贊揚共產?"},{"pid":"2831f61ab174f31899e2595cb7b49d5fbb70e5dc","tid":2116592,"uid":126731,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T09: